[block=center id=joining][size=18]Joining[/size][/block]\

[url=/p/messages?op=new&to=SzieberthAdam]Conact with the staff[/url] to get a set of stones.

Once you have your stones you have to apply them to this league. Members of this league can apply to tournaments in the [url=/p/group?op=view&group=10771]Luckboard Tournaments[/url] group. That group kicks all members once a tournament starts which is the reason to requesting a separate application. We need our members listed somewhere to have our banner in the [url=https://fumbbl.com/p/groups]FUMBBL Groups[/url] page.

Joined members are also invited to the Luckboard Discord group.


