[block=center id=rules][size=18]Rules[/size][/block]\

Rules correspond to Fantasy Football's. Below are the default client settings:\
[ulist]\
[li]No cards.
[li]Fouling is done with +1 on injury if the fouler is not interfered.
[li]Sneaky Git functions as Guard on foul assists.
[li]Banned Sneaky Git players are sent to the KO box instead.
[/ulist]\
Note that individual tournaments may have different client settings.


